title: The Five Gods
author: SmokeyPeanutRic
pages:
#- In the beginnings, long before man, long before the first sun was born, before the Big Bang, there were The Five.§0
§0
§0Ka'ZlNoktl Najad§0
§0Adlek'Cija §0
§0Maree-Jukar§0
§0Dra'Gial§0
§0Ducar'Alustia
#- It is not entirely known what happened in those fateful days before time. But what is known, is that the Divine Five were trapped outside of time, in a seperate dimension where they lie in slumber. Waiting. Waiting until the opportune time to escape their
#- wretched prison. §0
§0
§0The Five eternal dieties lie in dormancy. awaiting their eventual return to our realm. With them they shall bring forth fiery and awesome destruction. From the heavens they shall descend, their image alone inducing madness in the minds 
#- of man. The Five Ancient Things are our salvation, they shall reclaim what was once theirs, and with that they shall reshape the universe as we know it. §0
§0
§0The Five do not share our pretentious views of right or wrong, good or evil, they only are. 
#- The Great Five are vastly beyond anything we humans could even dream to comprehend. Praise be unto The Five. §0
§0In our final days of existence, their names will be chanted, their images --however crude-- will be worshiped. §0
§0Bask in their eternal glow.
#- It is said, somewhere in the world at the lowest peak, there is a temple and deep within the bowels of the dark halls lies a pedagogue. The mighty Pedagogue, a cleric of the Great Five. §0
§0The Pedagogue will be freed from the restraints that keep it from 
#- teaching the most devot followers about the Five.§0
§0
§0Praise unto the Five. §0
§0
§0Many have attempted to locate the temple, but all have failed. Frozen and dark, the temple waits at the lowest peak of our world.
#- Praise the Five. They shall turn our universe into smolder, our very existence shall be torn asunder. Our primitive brains shall be violated in our final hours, and we shall finally be freed and know peace.§0
§0
§0All hail the Five
#- Nothing matters, nothing is forever, all will annihilated. The universe, the galaxies within the universe, the stars within the galaxies, the planets that orbit the stars, the species that live on the planets. What we interpret as life shall cease for 
#- eternity.§0
§0
§0
§0Darkness brought by the Five shall consume us, free us. §0
§0
§0Bask in the glory of the Five.§0
§0
§0We shall be freed. 
#- 